  "metadata": {
    "last_modified": "2026-03-06",
    "tool_call_log": false,
    "notes": "Named toolsets for per-model tool binding. Toolsets with always_active=false participate in hot/cold lifecycle. heat_curve[i] = heat after (i+1) calls; last value is cap. Decay: -1 per turn unused. tool_call_log=true (global default) enables saving tool call prompts+results to memory as inline ST rows between the user prompt and assistant response rows, sharing the same topic and sourced from the calling LLM. Overridable per-model via conv_log_tools in llm-models.json."
  }
